			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1134" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 20px;" title="Jay Link Stewardship Ministries" src="http://www.stewardshipweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/Jay-Link-Stewardship-Ministries.jpg" alt="" width="134" height="173" />A servant&#8217;s heart, a well written message and a passionate presentation style &#8211; that&#8217;s what you&#8217;ll get whenever you watch any of the excellent videos produced by today&#8217;s guest on the podcast, <strong>Mr. Jay Link</strong>.</p>
