		<itunes:summary>I love being the host of the Stewardship Weekly podcast!

In this episode I had the great pleasure of speaking with author Rob Kuban about his newest book “the Secret of Generosity”. Just released on Dec 1st, Rob has already been interviewed numerous times to share his thoughts on how love, worship and service are all interwoven into this broader topic of generosity.

I was first introduced to Rob through his blog ‘Dollars &amp; Doctrine’ when I followed a link from another site for a group referred to as the ‘Christian Financial Alliance (CFA). It was back in July and I was starting to actively seek new friends online with whom I could interact and learn from. The 20 points within the CFA (each one supported by numerous bible verses) that form the framework that each member agrees to adhere to were obviously chosen by Rob in a very careful manner to keep each writer accountable to God. The alliance is an excellent idea and hopefully it will attract more participants as more people are made aware of it.



