After printing his first book and starting the blog, Rob turned his attention towards his next work. Realizing that believers had become engulfed in the shallow, never-ending pursuits of the world, he wrote about how we can claim the abundant life God has promised us. Appropriately titled ‘Christ-Centered Contentment’, the pages are filled with wisdom on thoughts about true peace, overcoming difficulties, meaningful satisfaction &amp; the joy of choosing infinite gratification.

