		<itunes:summary>A special welcome to readers of Jen's ebook "Living Beyond Awesome"!
Since starting this podcast back in June of 2011, I've had lots of fun making new friends online through various blogs, forums and email. When I first heard Bob &amp; Jen interviewed on another podcast, I felt compelled to contact them. Right from the initial response I received back from Jen, I knew this episode would be something special!

