Jesus the Wise Coach

We then spend some time together looking at Matthew 6:19-21 and thinking about how and where we store up our treasure.

A good coach figures out what motivates someone and then uses that knowledge to drive them to achieve excellence!  That is exactly what we see the Lord doing in this passage.  God knows that we, as emotional beings, are motivated by rewards.  And the reward in this case is treasure!  (He made us and gave us those emotions).  Now He wants to use those emotions for our own good.

