In this episode, Larry shares two different thoughts that tie in nicely with our study of where you store your treasure.  The first discussion is on the world’s obsession with collecting ‘stuff’.  Materialism is the focus and distraction of the society we are living in. In the second, he looks at the vineyard parable and the misguided emphasis of seizing the inheritance - the here and now.</itunes:summary>
