		<description><![CDATA[Have you ever had to make a difficult decision concerning a major purchase?  Of course you have.  Who hasn&#8217;t? In this episode, we spend some time together looking at the start of Gideon&#8217;s public life as he gets ready to lead the nation of Israel.  As we well know, he was quite unsure of himself [...]<p>Be sure to visit the web site at <a href="http://www.stewardshipweekly.com">Stewardship Weekly</a>
