			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>The show this week picks up where we left off last week, with thoughts on who own it all.</p>
<h3>Show Contents -</h3>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>A detailed look at Moses coming down from the mountain with the stone tablets and his reaction to seeing the people worshipping the golden calf.  God&#8217;s reaction and Moses&#8217; response.  <strong><em>Exodus 32:7-11.</em></strong></li>
<li>We then consider the relationship between us, money and God.  Who are we slaves to?  The world has completely inverted the biblical structure &#8211; pushing God out of the picture and enslaving us to debt repayment obligations.</li>
<li>Special guest &#8211; <a href="http://www.ntm.org/wp/jason_bechtel/about/" target="_blank">Jason Bechtel</a> w New Tribes Mission</li>
