<p>This is officially episode #1 and I&#8217;m excited as we start this journey together!</p>
<p>I&#8217;ve been in contact with a number of people and have asked them to share their success stories so they can be included in the first few episodes.  The content for episodes 2 through 10 is starting to fall into place and, as the weeks go by, I&#8217;ll be looking to you for suggestions.  As the host, I want Stewardship Weekly to be a reflection of the listening audience.  As we get started, if you call the toll free voice mail line and leave a message, chances are really good that you&#8217;ll be included in the next show!</p>
<h3>Show Contents -</h3>
<ul>
<li>Opening and introduction</li>
<li>My life and personal testimony</li>
